From e64e70c265cdb64670b9aa1c6ebe5c1edd2d9d61 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: "Ryan X. Charles" <ryan@ryanxcharles.com>
Date: Sat, 30 May 2026 15:24:38 -0500
Subject: [PATCH 61/73] Install PDF print helper

The print button knocked and found no door,
So we taught each frame a helper more.
The dialog still hides in future fog,
But gray no longer eats the doc.
---
